name: Bondi Icons for macOS
description:
Bondi is a fresh, yet familiar take on macOS 11’s redesigned iconography.

It’s a set of 29 replacement icons for macOS 11’s stock system apps, meticulously designed to be consistent, all the way down to the 16x16pt versions.

--- Icons in this pack ---

- Finder
- Safari
- Mail
- FaceTime
- Messages
- Maps
- Contacts
- Reminders
- Notes
- Calendar
- Photos
- Music
- Podcasts
- App Store
- Settings
- Books
- Calculator
- Preview
- Launchpad
- Terminal
- Console
- Photo Booth
- Find My
- News
- Voice Memos
- TV
- Stocks
- Dictionary
- Font Book
